style.backgroundColor : background color of an element

eg: changing background color of html body

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>changing background color</title>
</head>
<body>
<button onclick="change_color('green')">green</button>
<br>
<button onclick="change_color('red')">red</button>

<script type="text/javascript">
	function change_color(color){
		document.body.style.backgroundColor = color;	
	}	
</script>
</body>
</html>
